===========================================================================
$NetBSD$

Please install the SMF manifest depending for the agent or master
as needed:

  svccfg import ${PREFIX}/share/smf/${PKGBASE}/puppetd.xml

or

  svccfg import ${PREFIX}/share/smf/${PKGBASE}/puppetmasterd.xml

Enable using svccadm:

  svcadm enable puppetd

or

  svcadm enable puppetmasterd

===========================================================================
